                                        <p class="_j_note_content">DAY&nbsp;1<br />
二零一五年二月二十八日<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10507.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="开平" target="_blank">开平</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/36866.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="恩平" target="_blank">恩平</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11479.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阳江" target="_blank">阳江</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14336.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="茂名" target="_blank">茂名</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12475.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="湛江" target="_blank">湛江</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a><br />
<br />
渴望走在路上的味道越来越强烈，一个人停下来时间久了，忙生活久了，心也怠了，而心里本来就不甘安分。<br />
行走的意义在于：发现自己想要的生活，寻找真正想要的自己。<br />
学生放寒假直至新年正月初八，节奏一直围绕着上课、音乐节排练、前期工作准备、学生活动筹备、表演。不停的紧凑忙转着，直到初九，学生们基本都开始回学校上课了，手头上的工作也可以暂时忙完，跟富拿了7天的假期，这才算真正闲悠放松下来。想法每个人都有很多，但真正迈开脚步的却很少。其实这次计划也算是计划了很久，心里徘徊了很久，因为下星期六早上琴行还要上课，学生的十几节课不能一一的请假，所以只有七天的时间。<br />
早上八点，闹钟响起，其实躺床上还不舍得拨开被子的我，脑里伴随着出发的情景幻想醒来，只是赖床的习惯还拉扯着身体不肯立起。<br />
再次清点昨晚收拾的行李装备工具用品，一番洗漱后就打电话给阿攀（本次的同伴），因为他的车子借给了还在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广州" target="_blank">广州</a>的朋友，所以还需要回琴行拿我提前叫另外一位朋友借的宝马BMW&nbsp;X6山地车。（￥998国产牛车，哈哈。）<br />
十点钟在琴行会合许久不见的攀后就<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E5%8F%96%E8%BD%A6" class="link" data-kw="取车"  target="_blank">取车</a>后吃了早餐就开始骑车到了义祠车站。买完票等上车。<br />
十一点半把车子简单拆卸装进了车底箱，随后搭上满是脚屎味的车厢上，人齐车动，正式开始再一趟不一样的旅程。一路经过<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11479.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阳江" target="_blank">阳江</a>，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14336.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="茂名" target="_blank">茂名</a>，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12475.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="湛江" target="_blank">湛江</a>，尽管都是陌生的道路陌生的面孔，回想起四月份单骑从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12810.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广西" target="_blank">广西</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10308.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南宁" target="_blank">南宁</a>一路往东到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10507.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="开平" target="_blank">开平</a>的路线，激动地坐不住不停，我希望，大海如梦般蔚蓝，我希望，大海如天空般辽阔。我希望。。。</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867813.html" data-pid="134867813">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:834px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/74/wKgBs1deRNqAdnwgAAHHwj86ziQ87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867813" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
在服务区吃了个泡面，这是毕业后第一个泡面，哈哈。带上骑行面巾继续上了车（不要以为我准备在车上骑车，是因为车上太臭了！</p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">），戴上耳机，看了几集《一席》，不知觉的就睡着了，缓缓醒来，已到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12475.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="湛江" target="_blank">湛江</a>。窗边的山峰与山间重叠相折，稻田与村庄互相接连，太阳渐渐与山尖相拥。<br />
<br />
下午五点到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64641.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海安" target="_blank">海安</a>，客车师傅帮我们买了两张水路船票，把车子从车底箱拿了出来组装好，往码头入口骑了进去扛上了大油轮，长这么大第一次还是第一次这么大的船。六点钟船缓缓的动了，船上的消费太贵了只能啃了点今天吃剩的面包</p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">。船越开就越快，海风也越刮越大。在船上认识了位定居<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12703.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="四川" target="_blank">四川</a>小伙，一路上和我们分享了好多<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的地方民族文化，好玩景点，特色的小吃美食。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867816.html" data-pid="134867816">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/75/wKgBs1deRNuAQbrTAAj3MayMFuk00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867816" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867817.html" data-pid="134867817">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:599px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/77/wKgBs1deRN-AIarlAADednKp_7k95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867817" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
七点半即将到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>秀英码头，临下船还邀请了我们骑车经过<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>的时候找他玩。谁知船也会塞，码头待靠岸船太多了，排队等了两个多小时，晚上十点终于下了船。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867818.html" data-pid="134867818">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:599px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7B/wKgBs1deROiAOrotAADyXJcuANQ77.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867818" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content">到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>第一印象，果然，连马路上一路都是椰子树而且全都长满椰子，真想摇几个下来。哈哈。按着计划路线骑了大概7/8公里到了骑楼<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65633.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="老街" target="_blank">老街</a>（找地道美食体现当地文化最好去处就是去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65633.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="老街" target="_blank">老街</a>。）找了间单车店修修还没怎么骑就出问题的“宝马X6”，谁知车店老板态度十分恶劣，再三祈求还是以打烊为由死活不肯给我们修，这时我真想xxx，瞬间对有淳朴热情好客性格的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>人感到了些许的失落。<br />
找了间了50元小旅馆，欣喜的是，老板娘十分善良好人为我们打点好房间。再次应证跟着我穷游是不会住到豪华旅馆贵旅馆的。哈哈<br />
一番挑弄奇迹的把单车弄好后洗完澡就下了楼找吃的了。在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10507.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="开平" target="_blank">开平</a>本该长裤厚衣的装束在这立马换上了沙滩裤拖鞋。之前在《行者》看到的几种小吃美食：抱罗粉（粉的味道口感非常特别，酸酸辣辣的，非常好吃。）、椰子清补凉（十几种配料的椰子糖水）、莲雾果都尝了，味道超级棒！下次如果有朋友去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>，这几样一定要尝尝，旅游找美食推荐大家去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65633.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="老街" target="_blank">老街</a>找，地道实惠，经济美味。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867819.html" data-pid="134867819">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7C/wKgBs1deROmAIiyoAAhxzl1OaEQ67.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867819" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867820.html" data-pid="134867820">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7C/wKgBs1deROmAQ90kAAn3XVnK1DM20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867820" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867821.html" data-pid="134867821">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7D/wKgBs1deROqAN8UHAAuz9LdHqj486.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867821" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867822.html" data-pid="134867822">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7E/wKgBs1deROuAbAJyAAw1NNbOerQ96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867822" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867823.html" data-pid="134867823">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:600px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7E/wKgBs1deROuAa0x-AAjNmIqbFdU93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867823" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
结束第一天的行程。<br />
<br />
<br />
DAY&nbsp;2<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>骑楼<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65633.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="老街" target="_blank">老街</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63564.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="云龙" target="_blank">云龙</a>镇-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>坡-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10443.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蓬莱" target="_blank">蓬莱</a>镇-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>市-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>镇（全长147km）<br />
<br />
早上六点天刚开始放亮，洗漱，整理衣物，下楼吃个馄饨面，正在买单，攀已经骑车先走了，这货，居然走反方向，哎，正所谓开头出师不利。果然，找回这只盲头乌蝇后，找条出发的国道居然走错好几次路，跟着导航找了半个小时，终于到达国道起点，正式开始第一天环岛旅程。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867824.html" data-pid="134867824">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7F/wKgBs1deROyAcf3cAAdkNLUaY2I10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867824" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867825.html" data-pid="134867825">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/80/wKgBs1deROyAfAs4AAVJqCPxMXI52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867825" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
越踩越热越踩太阳就越晒，第一天总是最累的，因为身体体能还没适应的过来，踩的还没到20km已经累的不行了，于是倆人停了下来把背包里的几个莲雾拿出来啃了，休息了一阵继续上路，一路上不到十分钟后面超过了一个骑行者。<br />
果然，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的天气就像女人，说变就变，早早还太阳晒爆了头，突然的天就哗啦啦的开始下狗屎雨了。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867826.html" data-pid="134867826">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/80/wKgBs1deRO2ALK9EAAZmWNILqrk08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867826" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
立马的穿上雨衣，骑了大半小时，天气又开始变身了，雨开始慢慢停了，越骑越热越骑越热，太阳又开始冒出来了，骑到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>坡，也到了午饭时间。吃完饭后继续下面的旅程，距<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>镇还有80多公里。而接下来的国道路况也是前所未遇到的，一路的上坡下坡上坡下坡上坡下坡上坡下坡，天也变得越来越毒辣。一路穿过椰子林，横过菠萝田，溜过槟榔地。到了下午四点多，翻过无数连绵的高山，跨过村庄。到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10443.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蓬莱" target="_blank">蓬莱</a>镇，又是不断地波浪型下坡，脚越来越重，力越使越不足，原本以为体力不足到极限了，突然身后的攀喊着：“爆胎了。”往轮子瞧了瞧，轮子气已经漏的完全干扁了。结果买了很久祈求一直都用不上的补胎修理工具还是用上了。两人合力搞了大半小时，终于修好了，从未下手修理过，没想到竟如此的顺利的弄好了，打好了气继续出发。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867827.html" data-pid="134867827">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/81/wKgBs1deRO2AV7LpAAXB5rFlnXs86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867827" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867828.html" data-pid="134867828">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/81/wKgBs1deRO6AUd_7AAo5ytJzzrU03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867828" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867829.html" data-pid="134867829">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/82/wKgBs1deRO-AP_tnABJs-pvFTg866.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867829" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867830.html" data-pid="134867830">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/82/wKgBs1deRPCAZ5qVAAk8vO-g7-Q61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867830" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867831.html" data-pid="134867831">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/83/wKgBs1deRPGAeDakAA5uTKmbPAk30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867831" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
骑到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>市的一个小镇中心，买了点零食补充一下体能，也许就是这次车胎爆了，也许就是这次把422县道走错了走到421县道，也许就是缘分。这次并没有像以往的擦肩而过，没有像以往的是骑着山地车一屑不顾的骑行者，遇到了一位与其他骑行者不同的大哥，眼前这位骑着小小的折叠自行车，跟我一样大背包没放车架而是背在背上的大哥给了我一种亲切感，边骑边闲聊了一会儿，这位大哥姓李，来自<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12871.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="福建" target="_blank">福建</a>，现在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>工作，也是第一天来还<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛的，然后就决定一起结伴同行了。<br />
一起骑了大概两个多小时，经过潭门镇到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>，已迫不及待的溜到了海边。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867832.html" data-pid="134867832">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/84/wKgBs1deRPGATKbjAAg5Qy6M6Ug26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867832" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867833.html" data-pid="134867833">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/85/wKgBs1deRPKADYJwAAfcOyO_wqs24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867833" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
找到了李大哥上网订的酒店，执意的请我们住了一晚，作为礼尚往来我和攀请客吃了晚饭。一份椰子饭，一份烧鸡，一份菜，几杯啤酒，相识相遇的感激，旅途顺利的愉快。开心豪爽的干了几杯。逛了会儿夜市，又请了大哥尝<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>清补凉（城市做的完全不正宗，完全失败，一点都不好吃。）<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>骑楼<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/65633.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="老街" target="_blank">老街</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63564.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="云龙" target="_blank">云龙</a>镇-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>坡-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10443.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蓬莱" target="_blank">蓬莱</a>镇-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>市-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>镇（全长147km）<br />
<br />
早上六点天刚开始放亮，洗漱，整理衣物，下楼吃个馄饨面，正在买单，攀已经骑车先走了，这货，居然走反方向，哎，正所谓开头出师不利。果然，找回这只盲头乌蝇后，找条出发的国道居然走错好几次路，跟着导航找了半个小时，终于到达国道起点，正式开始第一天环岛旅程。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867834.html" data-pid="134867834">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/7F/wKgBs1deROyAcf3cAAdkNLUaY2I10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867834" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867835.html" data-pid="134867835">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/80/wKgBs1deROyAfAs4AAVJqCPxMXI52.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867835" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
越踩越热越踩太阳就越晒，第一天总是最累的，因为身体体能还没适应的过来，踩的还没到20km已经累的不行了，于是倆人停了下来把背包里的几个莲雾拿出来啃了，休息了一阵继续上路，一路上不到十分钟后面超过了一个骑行者。<br />
果然，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的天气就像女人，说变就变，早早还太阳晒爆了头，突然的天就哗啦啦的开始下狗屎雨了。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867836.html" data-pid="134867836">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/80/wKgBs1deRO2ALK9EAAZmWNILqrk08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867836" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
立马的穿上雨衣，骑了大半小时，天气又开始变身了，雨开始慢慢停了，越骑越热越骑越热，太阳又开始冒出来了，骑到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11251.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三门" target="_blank">三门</a>坡，也到了午饭时间。吃完饭后继续下面的旅程，距<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>镇还有80多公里。而接下来的国道路况也是前所未遇到的，一路的上坡下坡上坡下坡上坡下坡上坡下坡，天也变得越来越毒辣。一路穿过椰子林，横过菠萝田，溜过槟榔地。到了下午四点多，翻过无数连绵的高山，跨过村庄。到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10443.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="蓬莱" target="_blank">蓬莱</a>镇，又是不断地波浪型下坡，脚越来越重，力越使越不足，原本以为体力不足到极限了，突然身后的攀喊着：“爆胎了。”往轮子瞧了瞧，轮子气已经漏的完全干扁了。结果买了很久祈求一直都用不上的补胎修理工具还是用上了。两人合力搞了大半小时，终于修好了，从未下手修理过，没想到竟如此的顺利的弄好了，打好了气继续出发。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867837.html" data-pid="134867837">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/81/wKgBs1deRO2AV7LpAAXB5rFlnXs86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867837" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867838.html" data-pid="134867838">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/81/wKgBs1deRO6AUd_7AAo5ytJzzrU03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867838" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867839.html" data-pid="134867839">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/82/wKgBs1deRO-AP_tnABJs-pvFTg866.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867839" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867840.html" data-pid="134867840">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/82/wKgBs1deRPCAZ5qVAAk8vO-g7-Q61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867840" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867841.html" data-pid="134867841">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/83/wKgBs1deRPGAeDakAA5uTKmbPAk30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867841" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
骑到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>市的一个小镇中心，买了点零食补充一下体能，也许就是这次车胎爆了，也许就是这次把422县道走错了走到421县道，也许就是缘分。这次并没有像以往的擦肩而过，没有像以往的是骑着山地车一屑不顾的骑行者，遇到了一位与其他骑行者不同的大哥，眼前这位骑着小小的折叠自行车，跟我一样大背包没放车架而是背在背上的大哥给了我一种亲切感，边骑边闲聊了一会儿，这位大哥姓李，来自<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12871.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="福建" target="_blank">福建</a>，现在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10099.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="上海" target="_blank">上海</a>工作，也是第一天来还<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛的，然后就决定一起结伴同行了。<br />
一起骑了大概两个多小时，经过潭门镇到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>，已迫不及待的溜到了海边。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867842.html" data-pid="134867842">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/84/wKgBs1deRPGATKbjAAg5Qy6M6Ug26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867842" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867843.html" data-pid="134867843">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/85/wKgBs1deRPKADYJwAAfcOyO_wqs24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867843" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
找到了李大哥上网订的酒店，执意的请我们住了一晚，作为礼尚往来我和攀请客吃了晚饭。一份椰子饭，一份烧鸡，一份菜，几杯啤酒，相识相遇的感激，旅途顺利的愉快。开心豪爽的干了几杯。逛了会儿夜市，又请了大哥尝<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>清补凉（城市做的完全不正宗，完全失败，一点都不好吃。）<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867844.html" data-pid="134867844">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/86/wKgBs1deRPKACqAIAAnDL0ya5M479.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867844" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867845.html" data-pid="134867845">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/87/wKgBs1deRPOAHg5gAAd7Y0gAOp086.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867845" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;计划着明天早上起来看日出，身体倦累的还是抵不过软床的诱惑，日记写着写着就睡着了。。。。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;DAY&nbsp;3<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>-龙滚-和乐-大花角-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>东澳镇-石梅湾-日月湾（132KM&nbsp;）<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;早上天还没亮调好6点半的闹钟就响起了，拉开窗帘，浑浊的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>把整个天空布满得喘不过气来，赏日出的计划又一度的破灭了。被我闹钟吵醒的李大哥也起了床，只有我旁边着只猪还在梦境里夹公仔。推醒了攀洗漱完后三人退了房就到了楼下的早餐店吃早餐。几天下来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的伙食给我的感觉就是，贵！坑！怪！张口咬着大包，突然店里面走出来两位戴着骑行帽的男女，然后多嘴的搭了几句话：“要骑去哪里？”“今天要到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62982.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="陵水" target="_blank">陵水</a>。”回答道。随后闲聊了一番，原来这两位是夫妻，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12871.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="福建" target="_blank">福建</a>人，跟李大哥是老乡。也是从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>骑过来，沿着<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/27870.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="东海" target="_blank">东海</a>岸线边骑边玩，今天第四天。然后大家就决定一同结伴同行了。（又“捡”了两位骑友，哈哈。）<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867846.html" data-pid="134867846">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/88/wKgBs1deRPSAUC9HAAZ0_vsCJm488.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867846" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;吃完早饭，迫不及待的要出发了，又增添了两名队员，心里多少也添增了几份喜悦，（其实我还想去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>海边骑骑走走吹吹清晨舒服的海风，但算了，还是跟大队出发吧。）一路上也形成了一支小小的队伍，就在这时，李大哥突然停了下来让我们先走，说待会儿跟上。大队就继续往前骑，可走了大约两公里，回头看长而空的马路上依旧只有一两架汽车在走，并不见每次都在前头领队的李大哥的身影，觉得有点不对劲儿，于是大家都停了下来等候，可等了十多分钟还是不见踪影，然后我就往回路骑去。可骑了4/5公里超出了李大哥停下的路段还是找不到他，微信找也没有回复，这时攀打电话来：“先回来吧，他应该走岔路了，待会儿再找他吧。”<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867847.html" data-pid="134867847">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/88/wKgBs1deRPSAACX0AAT-gBv2ans29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867847" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;可人不和却也迎不来好地利好天时，沉沉昏暗的的天开始下起了雨。我也快马加鞭的骑来起来，走上几公里路翻过几个大坡再会和大伙们。而惊喜的是又增添了一名<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13061.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="新疆" target="_blank">新疆</a>大叔（付大叔）大叔今年五十，从西线<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62987.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="东方市" target="_blank">东方市</a>往东骑，今天第四天，而且还是第一次远骑环岛，太牛逼了。最后李大哥也回了微信说在龙滚镇会合。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867848.html" data-pid="134867848">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:800px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/88/wKgBs1deRPWABvX7AAacEb4bJBc26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867848" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867849.html" data-pid="134867849">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/89/wKgBs1deRPaAI6Q3AAqMrJt6DB450.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867849" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一路上风雨也开始交加，路况也不怎么平坦顺利。身推着风脸拍着雨的一路前行，背拉着地心引力脚搭着齿轮重力翻过一波又一波的山坡。雨渐渐停了的同时终于来到了龙滚，也终于找回了迷途羔羊李大哥，哈哈。然而感谢缘分让大伙们相遇，拿自拍神棍合照了几张。<br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;早上十点，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>人天气依然的变幻无常，太阳越渐晒人，路况也依然的一路成波浪状，让你体验下坡的轻松快感又把你拉到如攀登珠峰般艰难的上坡底下。&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867850.html" data-pid="134867850">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8A/wKgBs1deRPaABUwdAAmuMDhyN0M98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867850" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867851.html" data-pid="134867851">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8A/wKgBs1deRPeANsBgAAk-J-vhTLM73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867851" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;中午在和乐船家饭店上吃完饭，坐小船越到了对岸。吃得太饱了而又开始骑车小腹一直闹别扭，一路落后忍痛骑着。&nbsp;一路经过好多好多的村庄小镇，一路上活泼的小朋友不断的：“hi！、hello！、加油！”跟我们打招呼。<br />
<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867852.html" data-pid="134867852">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8B/wKgBs1deRPiAVuRGAAanL5tkHng51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867852" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867853.html" data-pid="134867853">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:338px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8D/wKgBs1deRPuAe15eAAID_RKWLvw20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867853" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867854.html" data-pid="134867854">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:338px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8D/wKgBs1deRPuAJpHuAAH5kJLt2ZA67.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867854" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867855.html" data-pid="134867855">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8E/wKgBs1deRPuAeqmWAAcOaaHweSc81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867855" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867856.html" data-pid="134867856">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8F/wKgBs1deRPyAJYubAAwSHCCfVf842.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867856" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一路的向当地人询问大花角的路线，骑了一个多小时，突然身后“bang”的一声，我转身回头看，德哥连人带单反摔了！摄影师不好当啊，在身后为我们拍照而单手拿车把被沙石绊倒，致敬！哈哈。停下来处理伤口，这时刚好停在一大片一大片的西瓜田边上，这时搞笑的一幕出现，李大哥都对着瓜田上喊道：“西瓜甜不甜~！（每次拍照的口头禅。）西瓜卖不卖？！”，“西瓜还没熟呢~！”农民回应道。哈哈哈~逗B。&nbsp;<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867857.html" data-pid="134867857">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/8F/wKgBs1deRP2ANBH2AA6vPkzYr5U42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867857" />
            </a>
                    </p>
                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这时离大花角海边之后几百米的路了，大伙儿处理好伤口后都迫不及待的继续前进，到了大花角，却入口却被军事基地挡住了，打算在外面拍几张照，却被里头的军人呵斥着赶走了我们，可错有错着，在旁边小沙滩上的伯伯说可以带我们抄小路进去，但要收我们车每辆两块的保管费。于是就艰险刺激的抄小路闯进了军事基地。到了大花角，顿时整个人廓然开阔，天啊，太美了，顿时秒杀了以往看过的一切大海。湛蓝的海水和蔚蓝的天空融合在了一起。清爽的海风拂过脸颊，所有的疲惫都忘却了。<br />
<br />
</p>
