                <p class="_j_note_content"><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;风景美不及人情美，冥冥中已经注定，遇到的每一人都有天意，感谢路上遇到的你们。<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
DAY&nbsp;4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
日月湾-分界洲岛-香水湾-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62982.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="陵水" target="_blank">陵水</a>-海棠湾-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>（137km）<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不要以为颠簸艰苦的长途跋涉后总能睡上甜美舒服的一晚，一整夜的停电把电蚊器风扇也停了，掀开被子，惹来无数蚊虫叮咬，盖上被子又热得透不过气，噩梦般的一夜。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;早上六点钟，海边的第一缕阳光透过窗檐洒进房间，从床上起来，几乎整夜没怎么睡。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一块走出海边看日出、拍照。遇到一位在海边搭帐篷<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12684.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="台湾" target="_blank">台湾</a>来的妹子，拉了过来一起拍照。<br />
</p>
                <p>
            <a target="_blank" href="/photo/12938/scenery_5513927/134867883.html" data-pid="134867883">
                <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:450px;width:600px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/31/A7/wKgBs1deRRKAOrdwAAZnQ3kDmyA14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="134867883" />
            </a>
                    </p>
